data.description: Welcome to your cozy home in North San Bernardino near Arrowhead Farms. This beautiful home has 2 bedrooms and 1 bathroom. The home has a great living room area that walks you into the kitchen. The kitchen area has plenty of space to host a dinning room table and more. The backyard has a new patio that was recently installed and the yard has cement and grass. Great amount of space in yard with a lot size of 8,400 sqft, you have plenty of room in the back to add an ADU. The home has a 1 car detached garage with a driveway that can 2-3 cars. Home comes with central A/C. The home recently got solar panels and a new roof installed with them. The home is minutes away from the University, the 210 & 215 FWY. The home is ready to move in! Come by and take a look!
